Do you ever doodle on your homework, or on tables, or just anywhere? If you did, give me an upvote, cause I like attention!

Just kidding. ,)

Well anyways, next time you do, take a close look at them! They can tell all about you!

Did you know that your doodles can determine your personality? Yeah, pretty cool, right?

Let's take a look at some of the most common things people doodle….

FLOWERS

If y’all love to draw flowers, it can show that you're a friendly person. You're also probably a more feminine person. Pointed petals show that you're a nice person though you may tend to act a bit cold. Rounded petals show that your family is important to you, and you’re openly friendly. A bunch of flowers show you have an extroverted side.



HEARTS

You love the idea of love, and you’re romantic. Bigger the heart, bigger the love!



LADDERS, ARROWS, & STAIRS

You’re ambitious, and you work hard to reach your goals. (You would never catch me drawing this, cause I’m way too airy, and I love to procrastinate. lol. )



YOUR NAME OR SIGNATURE

If this is something you draw pretty often, you lovelovelovelooveee attention, and maybe you’re self-centered. If you do this, you’re probably like, “I’m not self centered!!!” I just feel it in my fucking bones that you thought that to yourself.

Or you’re probably just practicing your signature.




PEOPLE

You have your life in order, you know what you’re doing, and you know what your emotions are doing. You’re in control of your life.




ANIMALS

Which animal do you draw most often? Well, you represent that animal, or at least you want to. Like drawing lions? You’re bold, or fierce. Like butterflies? You like your freedom. Like drawing snakes? You’re probably a backstabbing, unloyal bitch. Just kidding. ;)



FLAT SIDED SHAPES

You’re structured. You voice your opinions and you know what you’re doing, and you’re logical.




SWIRLIES

You like thinking. Your head is full of ideas, and imaginations.



SUN, MOON, STARS, ETC.

You’re a dreamer! You like fantasy and your head is in the clouds.



DRAWING EYES

Drawing eyes shows you’re cautious, and careful, and you may have a big personality!



This could go on forever, but I’ll stop. Hope y’all learned more about you or other people!!!

