United States and other countries. IN ENGLISH WITH CONFIDENCE is a trademark of ETS.
4.M2.partB_handout_transcript-of-audio.docxStudent I’m not sure if I ... oh, OK, I get it ... Yeah. And you know, another thing is, I
think people probably feel good about themselves when they’re at the gym. And
